title: LICTZNEE Jeggings for Women High Waist, Stretchy Jeans Slim Fit Leg Pull on Jean with Pockets, Soft Breathable Cotton Blend
description: HIGH WAIST DESIGN: The Jegging with slim style can well modify the shape of the legs, maintain a perfect figure, and show graceful curves. Simple and practical pocket, elastic waistband that does not bunch or twist.

COMFORT FABRIC: The stretchy denim is made of 75% Cotton, 24% Polyester, 1% Spandex. Elastic waist fit to meet different body types as much as possible. It brings you excellent elasticity, softness, skin-friendliness, breathability, full color and does not fade.
EASY TO MATCH: The Classic pull on Legging great to pair with your blouse, vests, shirts, sweaters, coats and so on, a must-have womens jeans in your wardrobe all year round.
OCCASION: The classic jean legging suitable for Casual, daily wear, outdoor, home, dates, parties, travel, vacation, shopping, street, party and so on. Women, ladies and girls are all available.
MACHINE WASH: Please choose one size up or one down according to your usual comfort level! Machine wash cold with like colors gently cycle or hand wash in cold water.
